        "collapsible_row_H4UzDp": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WARRANTY COVERAGE",
            "font_body": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>SEESON provides warranty coverage for eyewear frames (based on customer purchase records) with the following details:</p><ul><li>Frame front breakage caused by manufacturing defects is covered under warranty for <strong>1 year</strong>.</li><li>Metal coating components are covered under warranty for <strong>6 months</strong>. The warranty does not apply to peeling caused by direct contact with tables, chairs, or other surfaces.</li><li>Support for maintenance services including frame adjustment, cleaning, screw tightening, and polishing.</li><li>Normal wear and tear such as fading prints, scratches, loosening, etc. are not covered under warranty.</li><li>If a frame covered by warranty due to manufacturing defects is out of stock, SEESON may assist customers in exchanging it for another frame of equivalent value (no refund will be issued if the replacement product has a lower value).</li></ul><p><strong>NOTE:</strong> For warranty claims involving frames, SEESON does not provide warranty coverage for attached lenses.</p><ul><li>The warranty policy does not apply to products damaged due to improper use by customers or issues arising from lens fitting performed by third parties.</li><li>For damages resulting from regular use or beyond the warranty period, SEESON will consider repair solutions on a case-by-case basis. Applicable fees and processing times will be communicated accordingly.</li><li>Prescription lenses based on prescriptions issued by SEESON optometrists are covered under a <strong>30-day prescription warranty</strong>. Updated prescriptions must be verified by SEESON before warranty service is provided.</li><li>The prescription warranty does not apply to lenses made based on customers’ previous prescriptions or prescriptions issued by third parties.</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_9nMtfG": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WARRANTY SERVICE LOCATIONS",
            "font_body": true,
