            "row_content": "<ul><li><strong>Hanoi:</strong> SEESON FLAGSHIP Store — 44 Ton Duc Thang, O Cho Dua Ward</li><li><strong>Ho Chi Minh City:</strong> SEESON IRL FLAGSHIP Store — 199 Dien Bien Phu, Xuan Hoa Ward</li></ul><p>For warranty claims processed via shipping services, all associated shipping costs will be borne by the customer.</p>",
